38#ifndef _SASLC_PRIVATE_H_
39#define _SASLC_PRIVATE_H_
40
41#include <saslc.h>
42#include <stdint.h>
43
44#include "dict.h"
45#include "error.h"
46#include "mech.h"
47
48/** library context structure */
49struct saslc_t {
50 char *appname; /* application name */
51 char *pathname; /* location of config files */
52 saslc__dict_t *prop; /* configuration options */
53 saslc__mech_list_t *mechanisms; /* avaiable mechanisms */
54 uint32_t refcnt; /* reference count */
55 saslc__error_t err; /* error */
56};
57
58/** session context structure */
59struct saslc_sess_t {
60 saslc_t *context; /* library context */
61 const saslc__mech_t *mech; /* mechanism */
62 void *mech_sess; /* mechanism session */
63 saslc__dict_t *prop; /* session properties */
64 saslc__error_t err; /* error info */
65 uint32_t flags; /* session flags */
66#define SASLC_FLAGS_BASE64_IN 0x0001
67#define SASLC_FLAGS_BASE64_OUT 0x0002
68#define SASLC_FLAGS_BASE64 \
69 (SASLC_FLAGS_BASE64_IN | SASLC_FLAGS_BASE64_OUT)
70#define SASLC_FLAGS_DEFAULT SASLC_FLAGS_BASE64
71};
72
73#endif /* ! _SASLC_PRIVATE_H_ */
